item.title: Julian Carrasquillo
item.description: TECHNICAL SKILLS R PROGRAMMING LANGUAGE Tidyverse suite for data importing, wrangling, analysis, and visualization. RMarkdown, Shiny, and Flexdashboard for interactive and appealing report generation. Growing toolbox in text mining techniques, machine learning methods, API connections, and Git version control. STATISTICS Experienced in p-values, hypothesis testing, random sampling, and power analysis. Passed SOA professional Actuarial exams Probability P/1 and Financial Mathematics FM/2, both of which have historical passing rates less than 40%.
